204
00:08:52,648 --> 00:08:54,138
Then I'm sure it will be a girl.

205
00:08:54,818 --> 00:08:57,478
I don't understand how
you could be so sure.

206
00:08:57,988 --> 00:08:59,818
I'm sorry. I got carried away.

207
00:09:00,088 --> 00:09:03,678
Don't worry.
Wallpaper can be changed anytime.

208
00:09:04,558 --> 00:09:07,618
