225
00:09:55,638 --> 00:09:57,128
Did you lose weight?

226
00:09:59,048 --> 00:10:01,018
Mhm. About three kilos.

227
00:10:01,448 --> 00:10:03,308
Is your morning sickness that bad?

228
00:10:03,618 --> 00:10:06,788
But I've been feeling a lot better
these past two, three days,

229
00:10:06,788 --> 00:10:09,278
perhaps because of the change
in atmosphere after moving.

230
00:10:09,618 --> 00:10:12,788
Besides I was getting a bit chubby,
so it's perfect now.

231
00:10:12,858 --> 00:10:14,418
I guess so.

232
00:10:15,558 --> 00:10:19,028
