In fact, I tend to gain weight easily!

236
00:10:25,568 --> 00:10:27,238
My mom and older sister
are both chubby,

237
00:10:27,238 --> 00:10:31,008
and my younger sister goes through
great effort to maintain her great figure.

238
00:10:31,308 --> 00:10:33,278
